itics/403002-posle-prodolzhitelnyh-debatov-sejm-latvii-priznal-golodomor-genocidom-ukraincev|date=March 13, 2008}}\n* {{citation|ref={{harvid|Victims of Communism Memorial Foundation|2010}}|title=A Moral Blind Spot|url=https://www.victimsofcommunism.org/history_communism.php|publisher=Victims of Communism Memorial Foundation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100131150410/http://www.victimsofcommunism.org/history_communism.php|archivedate=January 31, 2010}}\n* {{citation|ref={{harvid|UNPO|2004}}|title=Chechnya: European Parliament recognises the genocide of the Chechen People in 1944|url=http://www.unpo.org/article/438|publisher=Unrepresented Nations and Peoples Organization|date=February 27, 2004|accessdate=May 23, 2012|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120604125012/http://www.unpo.org/article/438|archivedate=June 4, 2012|df=mdy-all}}\n* {{citation|ref={{harvid|ERR2|2018}}|title=Cornerstone laid for new memorial for victims of communist crimes|url=https://news.err.ee/828730/cornerstone-laid-for-new-memorial-for-victims-of-communist-crimes|publisher=ERR News|date=May 4, 2018}}\n* {{citation|ref={{harvid|BBC|2008a}}|title=Court Sentences Mengistu to Death|publisher=[[BBC]]|date=May 26, 2008|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/7420212.stm}}\n* {{citation|ref={{harvid|IHT|2007}}|title=Estonian charged with Communist genocide|url=http://www.b92.net/eng/news/globe-article.php?yyyy=2007&mm=08&dd=23&nav_category=117&version=print|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607181514/http://www.b92.net/eng/news/globe-article.php?yyyy=2007&mm=08&dd=23&nav_category=117&version=print|archivedate=June 7, 2011|newspaper=[[International Herald Tribune]]|date=August 23, 2007}}\n* {{citation|ref={{harvid|HRW|1999}}|title=Ethiopian Dictator Mengistu Haile Mariam|publisher=[[Human Rights Watch]]|date=November 24, 1999}}\n* {{citation|ref={{harvid|BalticGuide}}|title=Entisen presidentin serkkua syytet\u00e4\u00e4n neuvostoajan kyydityksist\u00e4|url=http