alth.nsw.gov.au/news/Pages/20200322_00.aspx |title=COVID-19 (Coronavirus) statistics|work=NSW Government |date= |access-date=23 March 2020}}</ref> \n| \n| \n| \n| 7 March 2020<ref name=\"ship-voyager-of-the-seas-first\" />\n| [[Sydney Harbor]], [[Sydney, Australia]]<ref name=\"ship-voyager-of-the-seas-first\" />\n| Royal Caribbean<ref name=\"cruise-owner-voyager-of-the-seas\">{{cite web |url=https://www.royalcaribbean.com/cruise-ships/voyager-of-the-seas |title=Voyager of the Seas|work=Royal Caribbean |date= |access-date=23 March 2020}}</ref>   \n| \n| \n| \n|-\n\n| {{ship||Grand Princess}}\n| 2,422<ref name=\"ship-grand-princess\">{{cite web |url=https://www.princess.com/news/notices_and_advisories/notices/grand-princess-updates.html |title=Grand Princess Update (March 6, 2020)|work=Princess.com |date= 16 March 2020|access-date=16 March 2020}}</ref>\n| 1,111<ref name=\"ship-grand-princess\" />\n| 3,533<ref name=\"ship-grand-princess\" />\n| 9 March 2020<ref name=\"ship-grand-princess\" />\n| [[Port of Oakland]], [[Oakland, California]]<ref name=\"ship-grand-princess\" />\n| [[Princess Cruises]] (a subsidiary of [[Carnival Corporation & plc|Carnival Corporation]])<ref name=\"ship-grand-princess\" />\n| 1,103\n| 103\n| 2<ref name=Hines2020-03-25/>\n|-\n\n| {{ship||Silver Shadow|ship|2}}\n| 318<ref name=\"ship-silver-shadow\">{{cite web |url=https://www.scmp.com/news/world/americas/article/3075208/coronavirus-cruise-ship-docked-isolation-brazil-operators |title=Coronavirus: cruise ship docked in isolation in Brazil, as operators suspend trips out of US|work=South China Morning Post |date= |access-date=16 March 2020}}</ref>        \n| 291<ref name=\"ship-silver-shadow\" />  \n| 609    \n| 12 March 2020   \n| [[Recife Port]], [[Recife, Brazil]]<ref name=\"ship-silver-shadow\" />           \n| [[Silversea Cruises]] (part of [[Royal Caribbean Cruises|Royal Caribbean]])<ref name=\"cruise-owner-silversea-royalcaribbean\">{{cite web |url=https://www.silversea.com/other-resou